"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"     </tbody>",
"    </table>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     AC: before meals; HS: bedtime.",
"     <br>",
"      * In this system, we assume that lean type 1 diabetes patients are likely to be insulin sensitive, while obese type 2 diabetes patients are likely to be insulin resistant. All other patients fall into the remaining group.",
"     </br>",
